snippet.title: [c64] Live and Let Die (1988)
snippet.description:
I'm demonstrating all four levels. This is similar with: "Buggy Boy", "Roadblaster", "Overlander" and most similar to an arcade game called "Hydra" (released by Atari Games / Midway in 1990) which was also later released for c64 (1991 by Domark). I don't like the music by Mark Cooksey in this game.

Published by Domark / Elite

http://www.lemon64.com/games/details.php?ID=1529
